data.description: Great starter house in South Fayette School District! This cozy home is well maintained and move-in ready with lots of updates: new windows, fresh paint and new flooring throughout. The bright and clean kitchen has ample storage, a functional layout and lots of natural light. The spacious living room is just waiting for your big, comfy couch. The main floor is completed with a convenient half bath and a bedroom. Upstairs you'll find the home's full bath, as well as a large bedroom and additional captive bedroom that would make a perfect nursery, walk in closet, work from home office or work out space. Full, dry basement. Enjoy summer fun with just the right amount of yard for kids or pups while still being low maintenance. The home's exterior is freshly power washed and ready for new paint. Close to shopping, dining, 50 and 79. FHA/VA buyers welcome!
